{"tid":1740540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"9up 買定離手，有幾多高官會辭職?","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:09:54.000Z","uid":4503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37e9f83de9402ce21af34bc605aec15d06aa668c","tid":1740540,"uid":4503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"Copy form <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/cml/civil/13.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fcml%2Fcivil%2F13.htm&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=0861e3dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/cml/civil/13.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最大熱<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長\t張建宗議員，大紫荊勳賢，G.B.S.，J.P.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓王好多資產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長\t陳茂波議員，大紫荊勳賢，G.B.S.，M.H.，J.P.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來博緊做特首 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長\t鄭若驊議員，G.B.S.，S.C.，J.P.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face